# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0000017> (bodily mobility function)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0000017> "A function that inheres in an organism and that is complex, being comprised of a bodily movement function and a motor control function, and that is realized by locomotion."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0000017> "William R. Hogan"@en)
