AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0010001> "An institutional health care role that is created by training and certification in physical therapy and that is realized by the provision of physical therapy."@en)
