AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0010004> "An activity of daily living assistive device whose function is to improve the degree of realization of an organism's capability for locomotion."@en)
