AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0010006> "An object manufactured with the function to enhance an organism's capability to grasp or hold onto other objects."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0010006> "It is not the case that every grasping or holding device is a medical device, so we put them under object. For example, you can buy a reacher at a big box store that is not registered with the FDA."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0010006> "Manoj Purohit"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000233> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0010006> <https://github.com/mcwdsi/rehabo/issues/67>)
