AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0010007> "A locomotion assistive device that (1) supports the body in a seated position, (2) has two or more wheels as part, and (3) whose locomotion function, if realized, is realized by a process that has as part rotating of its wheels."@en)
