# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011011> (physical exercise)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011011> "A bodily process that is intentional, has an objective of increasing the functioning of some part(s) of the body, is repetitive, and has one or more components of the musculoskeletal system as participants."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011011> "Maxwell Pena"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000233> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011011> <https://github.com/mcwdsi/rehabo/issues/41>)
AnnotationAssertion(dcterms:contributor <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011011> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9881-1017>)
AnnotationAssertion(dcterms:contributor <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011011> <https://orcid.org/0009-0001-9103-9263>)
AnnotationAssertion(dcterms:created <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011011> "2026-04-14T12:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime)
AnnotationAssertion(dcterms:creator <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011011> <https://orcid.org/0009-0004-2778-114X>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasBroadSynonym> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011011> "excersise"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011011> "Exercise is always goal directed, and that goal or objective is the improvement of the functioning of some part of the body. That part of the body is not always the musculoskeletal system. For example, cardio exercise improves the functioning of the heart and other components of the cardiovascular system. Plus, many exercises improve proprioception and cerebellar and other nervous system functions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011011> "Exercise is repetitive, and the repetition is typically if not always required to realize the planned improvement in functioning."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011011> "Isometric exercises like planking rule out movement of the body, or a part of it, as a requirement."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011011> "Passive ROM exercises rule out active muscle contraction as a requirement."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011011> "We do not capture “mental exercises” here intentionally."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011011> "physical exercise"@en)
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011011> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OGMS_0000060>)
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011011> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000055> ObjectIntersectionOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000017> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0000059> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000104>))))

