AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011012> "A physical exercise whose objective is to maintain the range of motion function of a joint or improve it towards clinically normal (when not currently normal) and whose repetitions are range of motion processes"@en)
