AnnotationAssertion(dcterms:creator <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011012> <https://orcid.org/0009-0004-2778-114X>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011012> "range of motion exercise"@en)
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011012> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/REHABO_0011011>)

